    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I like the Apache Commons IO library. Take a look at its version of <a href=\"https://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-io/javadocs/api-2.5/org/apache/commons/io/output/ByteArrayOutputStream.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">ByteArrayOutputStream</a>, which has a <code>toString(String enc)</code> method as well as <code>toByteArray()</code>. Using existing and trusted components like the Commons project lets your code be smaller and easier to extend and repurpose.</p>\n"
